songs.title: Train Wreck
songs.lyrics:
Here's you
Here's you
Alright here's you
I'm gonna do-
I'm gonna do an impression of you alright
Here's you

Choo choo!
Choo choo!
Chugga chugga chugga chugga chugga chugga
OH
*explosion sounds*
BUDUBUBUDUDBUDBUBUBDBUDBUBUD
BUBUBUBUBUBUBU
*another explosion*
MILLIONS ARE DEAD

Jon: Are you calling me a train wreck? *wheeze*

Arin: I was more implying that you're derailing

*both laugh*
